      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable dings, some paint fading on the hood, and a few scuffs on the bumpers, while the interior shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and carpet. Mechanically, it runs and drives fine, but it will likely need some routine maintenance soon, such as new brake pads and a suspension tune-up. It is a solid, functional car for someone looking for affordable transportation without the expectation of perfection.",
