    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly showroom condition. This specimen has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards, preserving its original luster and mechanical integrity. With its flawless exterior and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new, this car represents the pinnacle of its class. For the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48900.0,
